content_html:
A meeting took place between Prime Minister Sushila Karki and the Chinese Ambassador to Nepal, Chen Song. This meeting occurred shortly after a telephone conversation between Prime Minister Karki and Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi.

Chinese Ambassador's Assurance
